{
  "stem": "1530.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 163,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--has taught her at home-- taught him at home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 164,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 165,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, well, then when he was old-- yes, he went to cheder, reluctantly.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 165,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He never wanted to go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 165,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he went to yeshiva.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 165,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And occasionally, he was on top, the best student.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 165,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then he would leave it and become more modern.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 165,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, take--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 166,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we didn't call it Hasidic, because it was like one grade away from it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 166,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I don't know what they would call it, but--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 167,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 167,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, but he pushed it up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 167,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father pushed it up too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 167,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my father didn't wear a shtreimel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 167,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He wore a beaver hat.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 168,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A shtreimel is the most Orthodox, which is very similar to what the Russian Jews wore, whom we never knew.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 168,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's a velvet cap with, I think-- I think fur, which was a very good fur.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 169,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mink all around it, but my father didn't believe in that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 170,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A beaver hat is very much like a very fine-- and hat made out of, I guess, beaver or something, but it's not-- it wasn't furry.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 171,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he-- it was-- kind of looked good on him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 171,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was not--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 172,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But it wasn't the kind of hat that the Hungarian--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 173,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hasidim.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 174,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, no, no, no, no.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 175,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They could tell--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 176,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It-- yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 176,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a businessman--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 177,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--and he looked good.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 177,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He didn't look like a real Hassid.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 177,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He had a beard, and he had his payots pulled up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 177,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he had--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 178,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, something like that, with an umbrella, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 179,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 180,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah but he wore a jacket, which was just not that long.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 180,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he would have an overcoat, a black overcoat, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 181,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, but I don't think they showed that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 182,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If I remember, that it was always hidden.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
